# MISC::GET_CONTENT_ID_INDEX

## Parameters
* **INT** contentIdHash

## Returns
* **INT**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Returns index of content id from the global hash table
if content id is not found, -1 is returned
